OL,3,CHuw Edwards may lose Eisteddfod honour
OL,5,FFormer BBC news presenter Huw Edwards
OL,6,Flooks set to lose an honour previously
OL,7,Fissued to him at the National
OL,8,FEisteddfod after he admitted last week
OL,9,Fto having indecent images of children.
OL,11,FA "process" has begun following calls
OL,12,Fto remove Edwards as a member of the
OL,13,FGorsedd of the Bards ` one of the
OL,14,Fhighest accolades in Welsh public life.
