OL,3,CHuw Edwards may lose Eisteddfod honour
OL,5,FIt comes as the veteran broadcaster
OL,6,Fpleaded guilty at Westminster
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday to
OL,8,Fthree charges of making indecent
OL,9,Fphotographs after he was sent 41
OL,10,Fillegal images by convicted paedophile
OL,11,FAlex Williams over WhatsApp.
OL,13,FA National Eisteddfod spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "A process has begun and it is
OL,15,Fnot appropriate for Gorsedd Cymru to
OL,16,Fmake any further comment until the
OL,17,Fprocess has been completed."
