OL,3,CHuw Edwards may lose Eisteddfod honour
OL,5,FNearly a week on from Huw Edwards'
OL,6,Fcourt appearance, a number of
OL,7,Finstitutions and organisations he was
OL,8,Fpreviously affiliated to in Wales have
OL,9,Fbeen taking actions to disassociate
OL,10,Fthemselves from him.
OL,12,FEdwards has already lost his position
OL,13,Fas vice-president of the National
OL,14,FChurches Trust, and Cardiff and Bangor
OL,15,FUniversities said they are reviewing
OL,16,Fhonours granted to him in the past.
OL,18,FPlaques were removed from Cardiff
OL,19,FCastle and a mural was painted over in
OL,20,Fhis hometown of Llangennech,
OL,21,FCarmarthenshire.
