OL,3,CHuw Edwards may lose Eisteddfod honour
OL,5,FSpeculation had been mounting around
OL,6,Fwhat the Eisteddfod will do after he
OL,7,Fwas inducted to the Gorsedd in 2022.
OL,9,FThe induction into the Gorsedd
OL,10,Frecognises individuals for their
OL,11,Fachievements and their commitment to
OL,12,Fthe Welsh language, Wales and its
OL,13,Flocal communities.
OL,15,FThey are usually given to those who
OL,16,Fhave succeeded in the fields of law,
OL,17,Fscience, sports, journalism, media,
OL,18,Flocal or national activities or the
OL,19,Farts.
