OL,3,CHuw Edwards may lose Eisteddfod honour
OL,5,FThey can also be awarded to people who
OL,6,Fhave passed special Gorsedd
OL,7,Fexaminations, have achieved a degree
OL,8,Fin Welsh, Music or a subject in the
OL,9,Fmedium of Welsh, or have won one of
OL,10,Fthe main competitions at the Urdd
OL,11,FEisteddfod or National Eisteddfod.
OL,13,FSomeone's status in the Gorsedd can be
OL,14,Fidentified by the colour of their
OL,15,Frobes.
OL,17,FThe National Eisteddfod is said to be
OL,18,Fthe largest cultural festival of its
OL,19,Fkind in Europe and offers a stage for
OL,20,Fpeople to showcase their talents and
OL,21,Fcelebrate Welsh language and culture.
